Text: Hillary Endorsed Donald Trump for President According to Wikileaks “I endorse Donald Trump”- I am Hillary Clinton and I Approve this messageary   Here’s Gary Franchi as he reports that that before running against billionaire real estate mogul Donald Trump for the presidency, Secretary of State Hillary Clinton told an audience at a private, paid speech she wanted to see more successful businessmen and women run for office because they can’t be bought.
